「但他可能失去的遠不止於此」。消息導致特斯拉股價跌5.3%，收報300.71美元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;法案勢將通過，美滙指數偏軟，暫報96.31；惟資金買入美債，美債息跌至4.248厘。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;恒指阻力24411&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;A股開市軟&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;港滙觸及7.85弱方兌換保證，接錢200億港元，&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;拆息會否上升？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31971665&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=19862201686864a3e6b4cda0_98846770"/><published>2025-07-02T09:33:26+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3a3c05dc2585d24e086a94507f111ced</id><title>高處不勝寒！都係買返過氣股王 386 算，恒指升左9000點佢仲係52週新底，贏唔到大錢㗎啦，只係當收息用‼️</title><updated>2025-07-02T09:36:00+08:00</updated><author><name>精神裁判</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-02T09:36:00+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573072114"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573072114"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="50" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_39.gif"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="50" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_39.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="50" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_39.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="50" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_39.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="44" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_27.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="44" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_27.gif"/&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="